(297, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'page', '{\"name\":\"About Us\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"slug_id\":\"41\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<shortcode>[about-us title=\\\"Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n an to\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao nh\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1i London\\\" subtitle=\\\"V\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i\\\" description=\\\"T\\u1ea1i About Us, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n an to\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao nh\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1i London. S\\u1ef1 an to\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 \\u01b0u ti\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i. V\\u00ec v\\u1eady, quy tr\\u00ecnh tuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1ecdn k\\u1ef9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u1ed7i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u00e1p \\u1ee9ng c\\u00e1c ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nghi\\u00eam ng\\u1eb7t. D\\u00f9 b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ebfn London v\\u00ec c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c hay du l\\u1ecbch, h\\u00e3y tin t\\u01b0\\u1edfng ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho b\\u1ea1n m\\u1ed9t k\\u1ef3 ngh\\u1ec9 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p gi\\u1eefa m\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ed9 an to\\u00e0n t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a v\\u00e0 d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc.{{NEWLINE}}Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m London theo m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n m\\u1edbi v\\u1edbi danh s\\u00e1ch c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ed7 \\u1edf \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i tuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1ecdn c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn, s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ecba c\\u00f9ng c\\u00e1c ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n an to\\u00e0n h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u. T\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n boutique \\u1ea5m c\\u00fang \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n sang tr\\u1ecdng ngay trung t\\u00e2m th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u00e3 chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb s\\u1eb5n nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t k\\u1ef3 ngh\\u1ec9 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i lo l\\u1eafng. H\\u00e3y ch\\u1ecdn About Us \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i \\u0111\\u00e1ng nh\\u1edb, tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n v\\u1edbi s\\u1ee9c h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a London.\\\" highlights=\\\"Kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 n\\u01a1i l\\u01b0u tr\\u00fa an to\\u00e0n tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao nh\\u1ea5t \\u1edf London.; \\u0110\\u1eafm m\\u00ecnh trong v\\u1ebb quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 ngay gi\\u1eefa tr\\u00e1i tim London.; Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o gi\\u1eefa sang tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n nghi.\\\" style=\\\"style-1\\\" button_label=\\\"Xem th\\u00eam\\\" button_url=\\\"\\/about-us\\\" signature_image=\\\"rooms\\/168439421305-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-9-copy.jpg\\\" signature_author=\\\"Vincent Smith\\\" top_left_image=\\\"rooms\\/168144758004-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-1-br-5.jpg\\\" bottom_right_image=\\\"rooms\\/168144758104-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-1-br-2.jpg\\\" floating_right_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-02.png\\\"][\\/about-us]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[why-choose-us title=\\\"We Offer Wide Selection of Hotel\\\" subtitle=\\\"Rio We Use\\\" description=\\\"Explore a variety of handpicked hotels with Rio We Use. Your ideal stay is just a click away. Book now for an unforgettable experience.\\\" right_image=\\\"services\\/skills-img.png\\\" background_color=\\\"#291D16\\\" background_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-05.png\\\" quantity=\\\"3\\\" title_1=\\\"Quality Production\\\" percentage_1=\\\"80\\\" title_2=\\\"Maintena