(424, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"cloud-pool\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"cloud-pool\",\"slug_id\":\"79\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Cloud Pool l\\u00e0 h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i v\\u00f4 c\\u1ef1c n\\u1eb1m gi\\u1eefa khung c\\u1ea3nh n\\u00fai r\\u1eebng v\\u00e0 thung l\\u0169ng xanh m\\u00e1t, n\\u01a1i du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 h\\u00f2a m\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0o l\\u00e0n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong l\\u00e0nh, t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 chi\\u00eam ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng nh\\u1eefng kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc b\\u00ecnh y\\u00ean gi\\u1eefa \\u0111\\u1ea5t tr\\u1eddi.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p data-start=\\\"555\\\" data-end=\\\"972\\\">Trong nh\\u1eefng chuy\\u1ebfn du l\\u1ecbch ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng, h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng ti\\u1ec7n \\u00edch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c du kh\\u00e1ch y\\u00eau th\\u00edch nh\\u1ea5t. Kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u01a1n thu\\u1ea7n l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u01a1i l\\u1ed9i, h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c khu ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng cao c\\u1ea5p c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u1edfng ngo\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea3nh quan thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean. Cloud Pool ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t n\\u01a1i nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady \\u2013 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i v\\u00f4 c\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a v\\u1edbi thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean, mang l\\u1ea1i tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o cho du kh\\u00e1ch.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"974\\\" data-end=\\\"1378\\\">Cloud Pool n\\u1eb1m \\u1edf v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed cao, m\\u1edf ra t\\u1ea7m nh\\u00ecn r\\u1ed9ng l\\u1edbn ra thung l\\u0169ng v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng d\\u00e3y n\\u00fai xanh tr\\u00f9ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p. T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e2y, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn r\\u00f5 r\\u1ec7t s\\u1ef1 y\\u00ean b\\u00ecnh c\\u1ee7a thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean khi nh\\u00ecn xu\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1nh r\\u1eebng b\\u1ea1t ng\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng l\\u00e0n s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng tr\\u00f4i qua t\\u1eebng ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai. Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i theo phong c\\u00e1ch v\\u00f4 c\\u1ef1c khi\\u1ebfn m\\u1eb7t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u01b0 k\\u00e9o d\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eadn ch\\u00e2n tr\\u1eddi, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c h\\u00f2a quy\\u1ec7n gi\\u1eefa con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u00e0 thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"1380\\\" data-end=\\\"1752\\\">Ngay t\\u1eeb khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ebfn khu v\\u1ef1c h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i, du kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea7u kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed trong l\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1t m\\u1ebb c\\u1ee7a n\\u00fai r\\u1eebng. Ti\\u1ebfng gi\\u00f3 th\\u1ed5i nh\\u1eb9 qua t\\u00e1n c\\u00e2y, ti\\u1ebfng chim h\\u00f3t v\\u00e0 khung c\\u1ea3nh thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean t\\u0129nh l\\u1eb7ng gi\\u00fap m\\u1ecdi c\\u0103ng th\\u1eb3ng d\\u01b0\\u1eddng nh\\u01b0 tan bi\\u1ebfn. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u1ed9t ng\\u00e0y m\\u1edbi b\\u1eb1ng v\\u00e0i v\\u00f2ng b\\u01a1i th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n l\\u00e0 ng\\u1ed3i b\\u00ean h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u00f4ng gian y\\u00ean b\\u00ecnh.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"1754\\\" data-end=\\\"2096\\\">V\\u00e0o bu\\u1ed5i s\\u00e1ng s\\u1edbm, Cloud Pool mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ed9t khung c\\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t khi nh\\u1eefng l\\u00e0n s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ecfng bao ph\\u1ee7 kh\\u1eafp thung l\\u0169ng. M\\u1eb7t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i ph\\u1ea3n chi\\u1ebfu \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng nh\\u1eb9 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ng\\u00e0y, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ee9c tranh thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean d\\u1ecbu d\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7y s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng. \\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nhi\\u1ec1u du kh\\u00e1ch y\\u00eau th\\u00edch \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh ho\\u1eb7c th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c m\\u1ed9t t\\u00e1ch c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea trong kh\\u00f4ng gian t\\u0129nh l\\u1eb7ng.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"2098\\\" data-end=\\\"2476\\\">Khi m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi d\\u1ea7n l\\u00ean cao, khu v\\u1ef1c h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng r\\u1ef1c r\\u1ee1 v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea7u tr\\u1eddi trong xanh. L\\u00e0n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong m\\u00e1t c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i mang l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3ng kho\\u00e1i, gi\\u00fap du kh\\u00e1ch xua tan c\\u00e1i n\\u00f3ng c\\u1ee7a ng\\u00e0y h\\u00e8. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng khu v\\u1ef1c gh\\u1ebf n\\u1eb1m th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd, n\\u01a1i du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i, \\u0111\\u1ecdc s\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n l\\u00e0 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1eddi gian ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"2478\\\" data-end=\\\"2798\\\">Bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u l\\u00e0 l\\u00fac Cloud Pool tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean l\\u00e3ng m\\u1ea1n v\\u00e0 \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ea5t. Khi \\u00e1nh ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n d\\u1ea7n bu\\u00f4ng xu\\u1ed1ng ph\\u00eda ch\\u00e2n tr\\u1eddi, b\\u1ea7u tr\\u1eddi chuy\\u1ec3n sang nh\\u1eefng gam m\\u00e0u \\u1ea5m \\u00e1p nh\\u01b0 cam, v\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed3ng. \\u00c1nh n\\u1eafng cu\\u1ed1i ng\\u00e0y ph\\u1ea3n chi\\u1ebfu tr\\u00ean m\\u1eb7t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean khung c\\u1ea3nh tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1eb9p, mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c th\\u01b0 th\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 b\\u00ecnh y\\u00ean cho b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 ai c\\u00f3 m\\u1eb7t t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"2800\\\" data-end=\\\"3126\\\">Kh\\u00f4ng gian xung quanh Cloud Pool \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a cho du kh\\u00e1ch. Nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc gh\\u1ebf d\\u00e0i, khu v\\u1ef1c ngh\\u1ec9 ch\\u00e2n v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1edf gi\\u00fap m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean theo c\\u00e1ch ri\\u00eang c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh. \\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00f2 chuy\\u1ec7n c\\u00f9ng b\\u1ea1n b\\u00e8, gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n l\\u00e0 d\\u00e0nh th\\u1eddi gian cho b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"3128\\\" data-end=\\\"3457\\\">Ngo\\u00e0i vi\\u1ec7c b\\u01a1i l\\u1ed9i v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n, Cloud Pool c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u du kh\\u00e1ch y\\u00eau th\\u00edch \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh. V\\u1edbi khung c\\u1ea3nh thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean r\\u1ed9ng l\\u1edbn v\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, m\\u1ed7i g\\u00f3c t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ee9c \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1eb9p. Nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ee9c \\u1ea3nh b\\u00ean h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i v\\u1edbi n\\u1ec1n l\\u00e0 n\\u00fai r\\u1eebng v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea7u tr\\u1eddi xanh lu\\u00f4n mang l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c sang tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 th\\u00e1i.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"3459\\\" data-end=\\\"3695\\\">Cloud Pool m\\u1edf c\\u1eeda h\\u1eb1ng ng\\u00e0y t\\u1eeb 07:00 \\u2013 18:30, mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn kh\\u00f4ng gian l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 du kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng k\\u1ef3 ngh\\u1ec9 c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh. D\\u00f9 l\\u00e0 bu\\u1ed5i s\\u00e1ng y\\u00ean b\\u00ecnh, bu\\u1ed5i tr\\u01b0a r\\u1ef1c r\\u1ee1 hay bu\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ec1u l\\u00e3ng m\\u1ea1n, n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y lu\\u00f4n mang l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u00e1ng nh\\u1edb.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"3697\\\" data-end=\\\"3912\\\">V\\u1edbi thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf tinh t\\u1ebf, v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n gi\\u1eefa thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean, Cloud Pool kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ed3 b\\u01a1i m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t d\\u00e0nh cho nh\\u1eefng ai mu\\u1ed1n t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng s\\u1ef1 b\\u00ecnh y\\u00ean v\\u00e0 v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a n\\u00fai r\\u1eebng.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"1\"],\"image\":\"places\\/1681380943dji-0082.jpg\",\"tag\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 7, 'cloud-pool', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:05:47', '2026-03-15 20:05:47'),
(425, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'post', '{\"name\":\"orchild-spa\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"orchild-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"80\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Orchid Spa l\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n gi\\u1eefa thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean y\\u00ean b\\u00ecnh, n\\u01a1i du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m c\\u00e1c li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u gi\\u00fap ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 sau nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y b\\u1eadn r\\u1ed9n.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p data-start=\\\"4228\\\" data-end=\\\"4623\\\">Trong cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v\\u1edbi nh\\u1ecbp \\u0111\\u1ed9 nhanh v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u00e1p l\\u1ef1c, vi\\u1ec7c d\\u00e0nh th\\u1eddi gian \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean quan tr\\u1ecdng. Nh\\u1eefng li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh spa kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u00fap c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng cho c\\u1ea3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 tinh th\\u1ea7n. Orchid Spa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o ra v\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho du kh\\u00e1ch m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian y\\u00ean t\\u0129nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i, ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng nh\\u1eefng ph\\u00fat gi\\u00e2y th\\u01b0 th\\u00e1i.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"4625\\\" data-end=\\\"4952\\\">Orchid Spa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean, t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng. Ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac c\\u1ee7a spa s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean nh\\u01b0 g\\u1ed7, \\u0111\\u00e1 v\\u00e0 c\\u00e2y xanh, gi\\u00fap kh\\u00f4ng gian tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean g\\u1ea7n g\\u0169i v\\u00e0 \\u1ea5m \\u00e1p. Khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0o khu v\\u1ef1c spa, du kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 t\\u0129nh l\\u1eb7ng v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n ngay t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"4954\\\" data-end=\\\"5305\\\">Kh\\u00f4ng gian b\\u00ean trong Orchid Spa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed tinh t\\u1ebf nh\\u1eb1m mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0 v\\u00e0 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i cho m\\u1ed7i kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. \\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng d\\u1ecbu nh\\u1eb9, h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01a1m c\\u1ee7a tinh d\\u1ea7u thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 \\u00e2m thanh nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea7u kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1m g\\u00e1c l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9n b\\u1ec1 c\\u1ee7a cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 d\\u00e0nh th\\u1eddi gian ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c cho b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"5307\\\" data-end=\\\"5678\\\">T\\u1ea1i Orchid Spa, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn nhi\\u1ec1u li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe kh\\u00e1c nhau. C\\u00e1c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn bao g\\u1ed3m massage th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n, ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, li\\u1ec7u ph\\u00e1p th\\u1ea3o m\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng. M\\u1ed7i li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u, gi\\u00fap c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i sau nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c c\\u0103ng th\\u1eb3ng ho\\u1eb7c sau nh\\u1eefng chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i d\\u00e0i.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"5680\\\" data-end=\\\"5971\\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt vi\\u00ean t\\u1ea1i spa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 lu\\u00f4n s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c t\\u1eadn t\\u00e2m cho t\\u1eebng kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. V\\u1edbi k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt massage \\u0111i\\u00eau luy\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 hi\\u1ec3u bi\\u1ebft v\\u1ec1 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, h\\u1ecd c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3i t\\u1ecfa c\\u0103ng th\\u1eb3ng, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n tu\\u1ea7n ho\\u00e0n m\\u00e1u v\\u00e0 mang l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c d\\u1ec5 ch\\u1ecbu cho to\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"5973\\\" data-end=\\\"6314\\\">M\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a Orchid Spa l\\u00e0 vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f3 ngu\\u1ed3n g\\u1ed1c t\\u1eeb thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean. Nh\\u1eefng lo\\u1ea1i tinh d\\u1ea7u, th\\u1ea3o m\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn k\\u1ef9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng nh\\u1eb1m mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t m\\u00e0 v\\u1eabn an to\\u00e0n cho l\\u00e0n da. H\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01a1m d\\u1ecbu nh\\u1eb9 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i tinh d\\u1ea7u gi\\u00fap du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n v\\u00e0 d\\u1ec5 ch\\u1ecbu trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"6316\\\" data-end=\\\"6606\\\">Kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, Orchid Spa c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian \\u0111\\u1ec3 du kh\\u00e1ch t\\u00ecm l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng trong t\\u00e2m h\\u1ed3n. Sau m\\u1ed7i li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 th\\u00e1i lan t\\u1ecfa kh\\u1eafp c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3. Nh\\u1eefng c\\u0103ng th\\u1eb3ng d\\u01b0\\u1eddng nh\\u01b0 tan bi\\u1ebfn, thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c b\\u00ecnh y\\u00ean v\\u00e0 tr\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u1ea7y n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"6608\\\" data-end=\\\"6899\\\">Spa c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0 thi\\u1ec1n ho\\u1eb7c th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n sau khi tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m c\\u00e1c ti\\u1ec7n \\u00edch kh\\u00e1c c\\u1ee7a khu ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng. Nhi\\u1ec1u du kh\\u00e1ch l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn k\\u1ebft th\\u00fac m\\u1ed9t ng\\u00e0y d\\u00e0i b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ed9t li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh massage nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng, gi\\u00fap c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi ngh\\u1ec9 ng\\u01a1i.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"6901\\\" data-end=\\\"7218\\\">Orchid Spa kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u1eefng li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n. Kh\\u00f4ng gian y\\u00ean t\\u0129nh, d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a v\\u1edbi thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean khi\\u1ebfn n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng cho nh\\u1eefng ai mu\\u1ed1n t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 t\\u00ecm l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng trong cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"7220\\\" data-end=\\\"7477\\\">V\\u1edbi t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 nh\\u1eefng gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u00f3, Orchid Spa kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01a1n thu\\u1ea7n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 spa m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0nh tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n, n\\u01a1i du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng nh\\u1eefng ph\\u00fat gi\\u00e2y th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 tr\\u1edf v\\u1ec1 v\\u1edbi tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u00e1i c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng c\\u1ea3 v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1eabn tinh th\\u1ea7n.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"1\"],\"image\":\"places\\/1681438385rectangle-460.png\",\"tag\":null}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 8, 'orchild-spa', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:07:11', '2026-03-15 20:07:11'),
(426, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"orchild-spa\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"orchild-spa\",\"slug_id\":\"80\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Orchid Spa is a wellness and relaxation space set amidst peaceful nature, where guests can experience therapeutic treatments that help restore energy and balance the body after busy days.\",\"content\":\"<p>In modern life, with its fast pace and many pressures, taking time to care for oneself has become increasingly important. Spa treatments not only help the body relax but also bring balance to both physical and mental well-being. Orchid Spa was created with the goal of offering guests a peaceful space to rest, restore energy, and enjoy moments of true relaxation.<\\/p><p>Orchid Spa is designed with inspiration from nature, creating a harmonious and gentle atmosphere. The architecture of the spa incorporates many natural materials such as wood, stone, and greenery, making the space feel warm and close to nature. As soon as guests enter the spa area, they can sense the calm and relaxation from the very first moments.<\\/p><p>The interior space of Orchid Spa is thoughtfully arranged to provide privacy and comfort for every guest. Soft lighting, the delicate scent of natural essential oils, and the gentle sounds of nature create a completely relaxing atmosphere. It is the ideal place to set aside the worries of daily life and spend time caring for yourself.<\\/p><p>At Orchid Spa, guests can choose from a variety of wellness treatments. Popular services include relaxation massages, body care treatments, herbal therapies, and traditional healing methods. Each treatment is designed to deliver optimal results, helping the body relax and recover after stressful workdays or long journeys.<\\/p><p>The therapists at the spa are professionally trained and always ready to provide attentive care to every guest. With skilled massage techniques and a deep understanding of the body, they help relieve tension, improve blood circulation, and bring a sense of comfort to the entire body.<\\/p><p>One of the special features of Orchid Spa is the use of products derived from natural ingredients. Essential oils, herbs, and skincare products are carefully selected to provide the best results while remaining safe for the skin. The gentle fragrance of these natural oils helps guests feel relaxed and comfortable throughout the treatment.<\\/p><p>More than just a place for body care, Orchid Spa is also a space where guests can rediscover balance within themselves. After each treatment, you will feel a sense of lightness and relaxation spreading throughout your body. Stress seems to fade away, replaced by a feeling of peace and renewed energy.<\\/p><p>The spa is also an ideal place to combine with other wellness activities such as meditation or relaxation after enjoying other facilities of the resort. Many guests choose to end a long day with a gentle massage treatment, allowing the body to fully relax before resting.<\\/p><p>Orchid Spa not only offers high-quality wellness treatments but also creates a complete relaxation experience. The peaceful atmosphere, professional service, and harmonious connection with nature make it an ideal destination for those who want to restore their energy and regain balance in life.<\\/p><p>With all these values, Orchid Spa is not simply a spa service but a comprehensive wellness journey where guests can enjoy moments of complete relaxation and return to a balanced state both physically and mentally.<\\/p>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Forms\\\\PostForm\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_lang\":\"en_US\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 8, 'orchild-spa', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:08:14', '2026-03-15 20:08:14'),
(427, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"cloud-pool\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"cloud-pool\",\"slug_id\":\"79\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Cloud Pool is an infinity pool set amidst lush mountains and green valleys, where guests can immerse themselves in the refreshing water, enjoy the natural atmosphere, and admire peaceful moments surrounded by the beauty of nature.\",\"content\":\"<p>During resort vacations, the swimming pool is always one of the amenities most loved by guests. It is not simply a place for swimming; in luxury resorts, pools are often designed as relaxing spaces where visitors can also admire the surrounding natural scenery. Cloud Pool is exactly such a place\\u2014an infinity pool designed in harmony with nature, offering guests a unique and refreshing relaxation experience.<\\/p><p>Cloud Pool is located at an elevated position, opening up a wide view of the valley and the layers of lush green mountains. From here, guests can clearly feel the peacefulness of nature while looking down at vast forests and soft clouds drifting across the mountain peaks. The infinity-style design makes the water appear to extend endlessly toward the horizon, creating a seamless connection between people and nature.<\\/p><p>As soon as guests arrive at the pool area, they will notice the fresh and cool atmosphere of the mountains. The gentle sound of wind through the trees, birds singing, and the quiet natural landscape help melt away daily stress. It is an ideal place to begin the day with a few relaxing laps in the pool or simply sit by the water and enjoy the tranquil surroundings.<\\/p><p>In the early morning, Cloud Pool offers a particularly magical view as light mist covers the valley. The pool\\u2019s surface reflects the soft morning sunlight, creating a gentle and vibrant natural picture. This is also a favorite time for many guests to take photos or enjoy a cup of coffee in the peaceful setting.<\\/p><p>As the sun rises higher, the pool area becomes more vibrant with bright sunshine and clear blue skies. The cool, refreshing water of the pool provides a pleasant escape from the heat of the day. Around the pool are thoughtfully arranged lounge areas where guests can relax, read a book, or simply enjoy their leisure time.<\\/p><p>In the afternoon, Cloud Pool becomes especially romantic and impressive. As the sun gradually sets on the horizon, the sky transforms into warm shades of orange, yellow, and pink. The last sunlight reflecting on the water creates a breathtaking scene, bringing a sense of calm and serenity to everyone present.<\\/p><p>The surrounding space of Cloud Pool is designed to offer maximum comfort for guests. Lounge chairs, resting areas, and open spaces allow everyone to enjoy nature in their own way. It is also a perfect place to chat with friends and family or simply spend quiet time alone.<\\/p><p>Besides swimming and relaxing, Cloud Pool is also a favorite location for photography. With its vast natural backdrop and striking pool design, every corner here can become a beautiful photo spot. Pictures taken by the pool with mountains and blue skies in the background always convey a sense of elegance and tranquility.<\\/p><p>Cloud Pool is open daily from 07:00 to 18:30, providing the perfect setting for guests to enjoy their holiday. Whether in the peaceful morning, the bright midday sun, or the romantic afternoon light, this place always offers memorable experiences.<\\/p><p>With its elegant design, stunning location, and relaxing atmosphere surrounded by nature, Cloud Pool is not just a swimming pool but a special destination for those who want to enjoy the serenity and beauty of the mountains. \\ud83c\\udf3f\\ud83d\\udca7<\\/p>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Forms\\\\PostForm\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_lang\":\"en_US\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 7, 'cloud-pool', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:08:58', '2026-03-15 20:08:58'),
