(452, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"About Us\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"slug_id\":\"41\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<shortcode>[about-us title=\\\"A relaxing retreat in the heart of nature\\\" subtitle=\\\"About us\\\" description=\\\"Retreat is created as a peaceful getaway where you can step away from the busy pace of everyday life and enjoy moments of relaxation while restoring your energy. Surrounded by lush greenery, harmonious nature-inspired architecture, and thoughtfully designed amenities, it offers guests a complete and refreshing resort experience.{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Whether you are looking for a relaxing vacation, a journey to recharge your energy, or simply a quiet time with family and friends, Retreat is always ready to provide a comfortable, private, and inspiring space for every guest\\\" highlights=\\\"A peaceful retreat immersed in nature.; Refined design that brings a sense of relaxation and privacy.; A comfortable stay with full amenities..; An ideal place to rest, relax, and recharge your energy.\\\" style=\\\"style-1\\\" button_label=\\\"Discover more\\\" button_url=\\\"\\/about-us\\\" signature_image=\\\"rooms\\/168439421305-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-9-copy.jpg\\\" signature_author=\\\"Vincent Smith\\\" top_left_image=\\\"places\\/1683775376-vbk0653-edit.jpg\\\" bottom_right_image=\\\"places\\/1684383802linh-phuong.jpg\\\" floating_right_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-02.png\\\"][\\/about-us]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[why-choose-us title=\\\"We offer a variety of accommodation options to suit every guest\\u2019s needs.\\\" subtitle=\\\"What We Offer\\\" description=\\\"We offer a variety of hotel options with different styles and price ranges, making it easy for you to find the accommodation that suits your needs and budget.\\\" right_image=\\\"rooms\\/168179031903-ferms-grand-mountain-suite-2.jpg\\\" background_color=\\\"#291D16\\\" background_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-05.png\\\" quantity=\\\"3\\\" title_1=\\\"High quality\\\" percentage_1=\\\"80\\\" title_2=\\\"Maintenance service\\\" percentage_2=\\\"90\\\" title_3=\\\"Product management\\\" percentage_3=\\\"70\\\"][\\/why-choose-us]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[services title=\\\"The Pearl of the Adriatic.\\\" subtitle=\\\"Luxury Hotels &amp; Resorts\\\" description=\\\"**English translation:**{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Currently, there is no prominent decoration. Maecenas has created an appropriate pricing level. The overall link structure is quite solid, providing efficiency and harmony in connectivity. The operating system functions flexibly along the main connection flow. Users can make adjustments in a flexible manner. At present, the pathway has been opened, helping to improve oper\\\" left_image=\\\"rooms\\/168439420905-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-5.jpg\\\" right_floating_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-02.png\\\" button_label=\\\"Discover more\\\" button_url=\\\"\\/about-us\\\"][\\/services]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[news title=\\\"Latest News &amp; Articles\\\" subtitle=\\\"Our blogs\\\" description=\\\"Stay updated with the latest articles, news, and information about travel, hotels, and exciting experiences to help you enjoy a more fulfilling journey.\\\" background_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-07.png\\\" type=\\\"featured\\\" limit=\\\"3\\\"][\\/news]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[newsletter title=\\\"Get the Best Hotel Deals\\\" subtitle=\\\"Newsletter\\\" description=\\\"Discover attractive offers and special rates when booking a room at our hotel. Enjoy quality services along with many wonderful benefits for your vacation.\\\" background_color=\\\"#F7F5F1\\\" left_floating_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-07.png\\\"][\\/newsletter]<\\/shortcode>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Forms\\\\PageForm\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_lang\":\"en_US\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 5, 'About Us', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:39:29', '2026-03-15 20:39:29'),
(453, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"Services\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"services\",\"slug_id\":\"42\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<shortcode>[service-list background_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-01.png\\\" limit=\\\"6\\\"][\\/service-list]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[services title=\\\"The Pearl of the Adriatic.\\\" subtitle=\\\"Luxury Hotels &amp; Resorts\\\" description=\\\"**English translation:**{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Currently, there is no prominent decoration. Maecenas has created an appropriate pricing level. The overall link structure is quite solid, providing efficiency and harmony in connectivity. The operating system functions flexibly along the main connection flow. Users can make adjustments in a flexible manner. At present, the pathway has been opened, helping to improve oper\\\" left_image=\\\"rooms\\/168439420905-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-5.jpg\\\" right_floating_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-02.png\\\" button_label=\\\"Discover more\\\" button_url=\\\"\\/about-us\\\"][\\/services]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[booking-form title=\\\"Book A Room\\\" subtitle=\\\"Make Reservation\\\" description=\\\"Make your reservation quickly and conveniently in just a few simple steps. Choose your stay dates, select the room type that suits you, and enjoy a comfortable getaway with our professional service.\\\" image=\\\"places\\/1685507832restaurant-2.jpg\\\"][\\/booking-form]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[testimonials title=\\\"What Our Clients Says\\\" subtitle=\\\"Testimonial\\\" description=\\\"Discover genuine stories and reviews from guests who have experienced our services. Customer satisfaction is always our motivation to continuously improve and enhance the quality of our service.\\\" background_image=\\\"\\/backgrounds\\/testimonial-bg.png\\\" testimonial_ids=\\\"1,2,3,4,5,6\\\"][\\/testimonials]<\\/shortcode>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Forms\\\\PageForm\",\"gallery\":nul