(454, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"Term and Conditions\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"term-and-conditions\",\"slug_id\":\"49\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"about-area5 about-p p-relative\\\"><div class=\\\"container pt-60 pb-90\\\"><div class=\\\"service-detail\\\"><div class=\\\"content-box\\\"><h3>Definitions<\\/h3><p>Some of the words you\\u2019ll see have very specific meanings, so please check out the \\u2018RioRelax dictionary\\u2019 at the end of these Terms.<\\/p><h3>About these terms<\\/h3><p>When you complete your Booking, you accept these Terms and any other terms that you\\u2019re provided with during the booking process.<\\/p><p>The English version of these Terms is the original. If there\\u2019s any dispute about the Terms, or any mismatch between the Terms in English and in another language, the Terms as they appear in English will apply. (You can change the language at the top of this page.<\\/p><h3>Our Platform<\\/h3><p>We take reasonable care in providing our Platform, but we can\\u2019t guarantee that everything on it is accurate (we get information from the Service Providers). To the extent permitted by law, we can\\u2019t be held responsible for any errors, any interruptions, or any missing bits of information - although we will do everything we can to correct\\/fix them as soon as we can.<\\/p><p>We will show you the offers that are available to you, in (what we think is) the right language for you. You can change to another language whenever you like.<\\/p><h3>Prices<\\/h3><p>When you make a Booking, you agree to pay the cost of the Travel Experience, including any charges and taxes that may apply.<\\/p><p>Some of the prices you see may have been rounded to the nearest whole number. The price you pay will be based on the original, \'non-rounded\' price (although the actual difference will be tiny anyway).<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Forms\\\\PageForm\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_lang\":\"en_US\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 13, 'Term and Conditions', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:43:39', '2026-03-15 20:43:39'),
(455, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'page', '{\"name\":\"\\u0110i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n & \\u0110i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"term-and-conditions\",\"slug_id\":\"49\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<h3>\\u0110\\u1ecbnh ngh\\u0129a<\\/h3><p data-start=\\\"42\\\" data-end=\\\"192\\\">M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 t\\u1eeb ng\\u1eef b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y trong t\\u00e0i li\\u1ec7u n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 \\u00fd ngh\\u0129a r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3, v\\u00ec v\\u1eady vui l\\u00f2ng tham kh\\u1ea3o \\u201ct\\u1eeb \\u0111i\\u1ec3n RioRelax\\u201d \\u1edf cu\\u1ed1i \\u0110i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 h\\u01a1n.<\\/p><h3>V\\u1ec1 c\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0y<\\/h3><p data-start=\\\"221\\\" data-end=\\\"376\\\">Khi b\\u1ea1n ho\\u00e0n t\\u1ea5t vi\\u1ec7c \\u0110\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ed7, b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u00fd v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c \\u0110i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0y c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cung c\\u1ea5p cho b\\u1ea1n trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ed7.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"378\\\" data-end=\\\"663\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n ti\\u1ebfng Anh c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c \\u0110i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3n g\\u1ed1c. N\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 tranh ch\\u1ea5p n\\u00e0o li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c \\u0110i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n, ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t gi\\u1eefa phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n ti\\u1ebfng Anh v\\u00e0 phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n b\\u1eb1ng ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef kh\\u00e1c, th\\u00ec phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n ti\\u1ebfng Anh s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng. (B\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1ea7u trang.)<\\/p><h3>N\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i<\\/h3><p data-start=\\\"693\\\" data-end=\\\"1122\\\">Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd \\u0111\\u1ec3 cung c\\u1ea5p v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh N\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh, tuy nhi\\u00ean ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o r\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ecdi th\\u00f4ng tin tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ec1u ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n ch\\u00ednh x\\u00e1c (v\\u00ec ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i nh\\u1eadn m\\u1ed9t ph\\u1ea7n th\\u00f4ng tin t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c Nh\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5). Trong ph\\u1ea1m vi ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt cho ph\\u00e9p, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ecbu tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 l\\u1ed7i n\\u00e0o, s\\u1ef1 gi\\u00e1n \\u0111o\\u1ea1n n\\u00e0o ho\\u1eb7c th\\u00f4ng tin b\\u1ecb thi\\u1ebfu \\u2013 m\\u1eb7c d\\u00f9 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd c\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng kh\\u1eafc ph\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ec9nh s\\u1eeda s\\u1edbm nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"1124\\\" data-end=\\\"1282\\\">Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb cho b\\u1ea1n c\\u00e1c \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i c\\u00f3 s\\u1eb5n b\\u1eb1ng ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef m\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cho l\\u00e0 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi b\\u1ea1n. B\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i sang ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef kh\\u00e1c b\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 l\\u00fac n\\u00e0o.<\\/p><h3>Gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea3<\\/h3><p data-start=\\\"1296\\\" data-end=\\\"1431\\\">Khi b\\u1ea1n th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n \\u0110\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ed7, b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u00fd thanh to\\u00e1n chi ph\\u00ed c\\u1ee7a Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m du l\\u1ecbch, bao g\\u1ed3m m\\u1ecdi kho\\u1ea3n ph\\u00ed v\\u00e0 thu\\u1ebf c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"1433\\\" data-end=\\\"1628\\\" data-is-last-node=\\\"\\\" data-is-only-node=\\\"\\\">M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 b\\u1ea1n th\\u1ea5y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u01