(460, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', '', '{\"name\":\"Privacy\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"privacy\",\"slug_id\":\"48\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"about-area5 about-p p-relative\\\"><div class=\\\"container pt-60 pb-90\\\"><div class=\\\"service-detail\\\"><div class=\\\"content-box\\\"><h2>Privacy Statement<\\/h2><p>First things first \\u2013 your privacy is important to us. That might be the kind of thing all these notices say, but we mean it. You place your trust in us by using us services and we value that trust. That means we\\u2019re committed to protecting and safeguarding your personal data. We act in our customers\\u2019 best interest and we are transparent about the processing of your personal data.<\\/p><p>If you\\u2019ve used us before, you know that us services offers online travel-related services through our own websites and mobile apps, as well as other online platforms such as partners\\u2019 websites and social media. We\\u2019d like to point out that all the information you are about to read, generally applies to not one, not two, but all of these platforms.<\\/p><p>If you\\u2019ve used us before, you know that us services offers online travel-related services through our own websites and mobile apps, as well as other online platforms such as partners\\u2019 websites and social media. We\\u2019d like to point out that all the information you are about to read, generally applies to not one, not two, but all of these platforms.<\\/p><h2>Terms we use in this Privacy Statement<\\/h2><p>\'Trip\' means the various different travel products and services that can be ordered, acquired, purchased, bought, paid, rented, provided, reserved, combined, or consummated by you from the Trip Provider.<\\/p><p>\'Trip Provider\' means the provider of accommodation (e.g. hotel, motel, apartment, bed &amp; breakfast, landlord), attractions (e.g. (theme) parks, museums, sightseeing tours), transportation provider (e.g. car rentals, cruises, rail, airport rides, coach tours, transfers), tour operators, travel insurances and any other travel or related product or service as from time to time available for Trip Reservation on the platform.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"form\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Forms\\\\PageForm\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_lang\":\"en_US\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 12, 'Privacy', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:52:57', '2026-03-15 20:52:57'),
(461, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'page', '{\"name\":\"Privacy\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"privacy\",\"slug_id\":\"48\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"about-area5 about-p p-relative\\\"><div class=\\\"container pt-60 pb-90\\\"><div class=\\\"service-detail\\\"><div class=\\\"content-box\\\"><h2>Tuy\\u00ean b\\u1ed1 Quy\\u1ec1n ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0<\\/h2><p data-start=\\\"79\\\" data-end=\\\"567\\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ebft \\u2013 <strong data-start=\\\"91\\\" data-end=\\\"150\\\">quy\\u1ec1n ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0 c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i<\\/strong>. C\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u1ea5y c\\u00e2u n\\u00f3i n\\u00e0y trong nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u00f4ng b\\u00e1o kh\\u00e1c, nh\\u01b0ng ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1 nghi\\u00eam t\\u00fac v\\u1ec1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u00f3. Khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i, b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1eb7t ni\\u1ec1m tin v\\u00e0o ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i r\\u1ea5t tr\\u00e2n tr\\u1ecdng s\\u1ef1 tin t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ea5y. V\\u00ec v\\u1eady, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft <strong data-start=\\\"398\\\" data-end=\\\"451\\\">b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 v\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef an to\\u00e0n cho d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n<\\/strong>. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i lu\\u00f4n h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00ec l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 minh b\\u1ea1ch trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"569\\\" data-end=\\\"1017\\\">N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e2y, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd bi\\u1ebft r\\u1eb1ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cung c\\u1ea5p <strong data-start=\\\"674\\\" data-end=\\\"708\\\">c\\u00e1c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 du l\\u1ecbch tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn<\\/strong> th\\u00f4ng qua c\\u00e1c <strong data-start=\\\"723\\\" data-end=\\\"776\\\">trang web v\\u00e0 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00ednh ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i<\\/strong>, c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1c <strong data-start=\\\"791\\\" data-end=\\\"819\\\">n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00e1c<\\/strong> nh\\u01b0 website c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 m\\u1ea1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i mu\\u1ed1n l\\u01b0u \\u00fd r\\u1eb1ng t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin b\\u1ea1n s\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1ecdc d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y <strong data-start=\\\"930\\\" data-end=\\\"1016\\\">kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng cho m\\u1ed9t hay hai n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng, m\\u00e0 \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng cho t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng n\\u00e0y<\\/strong>.<\\/p><p data-start=\\\"1019\\\" data-end=\\\"1411\\\">N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e2y, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd bi\\u1ebft r\\u1eb1ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cung c\\u1ea5p c\\u00e1c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 du l\\u1ecbch tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn th\\u00f4ng qua c\\u00e1c trang web v\\u00e0 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00ednh ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i, c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1c n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0 website c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 m\\u1ea1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i mu\\u1ed1n nh\\u1ea5n m\\u1ea1nh r\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ecdi th\\u00f4ng tin trong t\\u00e0i li\\u1ec7u n\\u00e0y nh\\u00ecn chung <strong data-start=\\\"1372\\\" data-end=\\\"1410\\\">\\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng cho t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u00f3<\\/strong>.<\\/p><h2>C\\u00e1c thu\\u1eadt ng\\u1eef \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong Tuy\\u00ean b\\u1ed1 Quy\\u1ec1n ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0 n\\u00e0y<\\/h2><p><strong data-start=\\\"1488\\\" data-end=\\\"1510\\\">\\u201cTrip\\u201d (Chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i)<\\/strong>: L\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0 d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 du l\\u1ecbch kh\\u00e1c nhau m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 <strong data-start=\\\"1573\\\" data-end=\\\"1646\\\">\\u0111\\u1eb7t, mua, thanh to\\u00e1n, thu\\u00ea, cung c\\u1ea5p, \\u0111\\u1eb7t tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p ho\\u1eb7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng<\\/strong> t\\u1eeb <strong data-start=\\\"1650\\\" data-end=\\\"1692\\\">Nh\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i (Trip Provider)<\\/strong>.<\\/p><p><strong data-start=\\\"1695\\\" data-end=\\\"1739\\\">\\u201cTrip Provider\\u201d (Nh\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i)<\\/strong>: L\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb cung c\\u1ea5p <strong data-start=\\\"1762\\\" data-end=\\\"1771\\\">ch\\u1ed7 \\u1edf<\\/strong> (v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5: kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, motel, c\\u0103n h\\u1ed9, nh\\u00e0 ngh\\u1ec9 B&amp;B, ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 cho thu\\u00ea), <strong data-start=\\\"1839\\\" data-end=\\\"1857\\\">\\u0111i\\u1ec3m tham quan<\\/strong> (v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5: c\\u00f4ng vi\\u00ean gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u00ed, b\\u1ea3o t\\u00e0ng, tour tham quan), <strong data-start=\\\"1913\\\" data-end=\\\"1935\\\">d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 v\\u1eadn chuy\\u1ec3n<\\/strong> (v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5: thu\\u00ea xe, du thuy\\u1ec1n, t\\u00e0u h\\u1ecfa, xe \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u00f3n s\\u00e2n bay, tour xe kh\\u00e1ch, d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 trung chuy\\u1ec3n), <strong data-start=\\\"2031\\\" data-end=\\\"2053\\\">nh\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00e0nh tour<\\/strong>, <strong data-start=\\\"2055\\\" data-end=\\\"2075\\\">b\\u1ea3o hi\\u1ec3m du l\\u1ecbch<\\/strong>, v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ho\\u1eb7c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 du l\\u1ecbch li\\u00ean quan n\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cung c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u1ec3 <strong data-start=\\\"2153\\\" data-end=\\\"2184\\\">\\u0111\\u1eb7t chuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111i tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng<\\/strong> theo t\\u1eebng th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"full-width\",\"breadcrumb\":\"1\",\"breadcrumb_background\":null,\"image\":null}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '203.210.138.33', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 12, 'Privacy', 'primary', '2026-03-15 20:54:22', '2026-03-15 20:54:22'),
(462, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'page', '{\"name\":\"FAQ\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"slug\":\"faq\",\"slug_id\":\"44\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":null,\"content\":\"<shortcode>[faqs category_ids=\\\"1,2,3,4,5\\\"][\\/faqs]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[newsletter title=\\\"Nh\\u1eadn \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t cho kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n\\\" subtitle=\\\"B\\u1ea3n tin\\\" description=\\\"Kh\\u00e1m ph\\u00e1 nh\\u1eefng \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn v\\u00e0 m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t khi \\u0111\\u1eb7t ph\\u00f2ng t\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i. T\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f9ng nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi cho k\\u1ef3 ngh\\u1ec9 c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.\\\" background_color=\\\"#F7F5F1\\\" left_floating_image=\\\"backgrounds\\/an-img-07.png\\\"][\\/newsletter]<\\/shortcode><shortcode>[teams title=\\\"Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t\\\" subtitle=\\\"\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i\\\" description=\\\"V\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 th\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1ea5t, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i t\\u1eadn t\\u00e2m t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean k\\u1ef3 ngh\\u1ec9 ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o cho b\\u1ea1n, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u1ecdi chi ti\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec1u th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n cam k\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc.\\\" team_ids=\\\"1,2,3,4,5,6\\\" style=\\\"style-1\\\"][\\/teams]<\\/shortcode>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"full-width\",\"breadcrumb\":\"1\",\"breadcrumb_background\":null,\"image\":null}', 'updated', 'Mozil