('en_US', 5, 'About Us', NULL, '<shortcode>[about-us title=\"A relaxing retreat in the heart of nature\" subtitle=\"About us\" description=\"Retreat is created as a peaceful getaway where you can step away from the busy pace of everyday life and enjoy moments of relaxation while restoring your energy. Surrounded by lush greenery, harmonious nature-inspired architecture, and thoughtfully designed amenities, it offers guests a complete and refreshing resort experience.{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Whether you are looking for a relaxing vacation, a journey to recharge your energy, or simply a quiet time with family and friends, Retreat is always ready to provide a comfortable, private, and inspiring space for every guest\" highlights=\"A peaceful retreat immersed in nature.; Refined design that brings a sense of relaxation and privacy.; A comfortable stay with full amenities..; An ideal place to rest, relax, and recharge your energy.\" style=\"style-1\" button_label=\"Discover more\" button_url=\"/about-us\" signature_image=\"rooms/168439421305-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-9-copy.jpg\" signature_author=\"Vincent Smith\" top_left_image=\"places/1683775376-vbk0653-edit.jpg\" bottom_right_image=\"places/1684383802linh-phuong.jpg\" floating_right_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-02.png\"][/about-us]</shortcode><shortcode>[why-choose-us title=\"We offer a variety of accommodation options to suit every guest’s needs.\" subtitle=\"What We Offer\" description=\"We offer a variety of hotel options with different styles and price ranges, making it easy for you to find the accommodation that suits your needs and budget.\" right_image=\"rooms/168179031903-ferms-grand-mountain-suite-2.jpg\" background_color=\"#291D16\" background_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-05.png\" quantity=\"3\" title_1=\"High quality\" percentage_1=\"80\" title_2=\"Maintenance service\" percentage_2=\"90\" title_3=\"Product management\" percentage_3=\"70\"][/why-choose-us]</shortcode><shortcode>[services title=\"The Pearl of the Adriatic.\" subtitle=\"Luxury Hotels &amp; Resorts\" description=\"**English translation:**{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Currently, there is no prominent decoration. Maecenas has created an appropriate pricing level. The overall link structure is quite solid, providing efficiency and harmony in connectivity. The operating system functions flexibly along the main connection flow. Users can make adjustments in a flexible manner. At present, the pathway has been opened, helping to improve oper\" left_image=\"rooms/168439420905-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-5.jpg\" right_floating_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-02.png\" button_label=\"Discover more\" button_url=\"/about-us\"][/services]</shortcode><shortcode>[news title=\"Latest News &amp; Articles\" subtitle=\"Our blogs\" description=\"Stay updated with the latest articles, news, and information about travel, hotels, and exciting experiences to help you enjoy a more fulfilling journey.\" background_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-07.png\" type=\"featured\" limit=\"3\"][/news]</shortcode><shortcode>[newsletter title=\"Get the Best Hotel Deals\" subtitle=\"Newsletter\" description=\"Discover attractive offers and special rates when booking a room at our hotel. Enjoy quality services along with many wonderful benefits for your vacation.\" background_color=\"#F7F5F1\" left_floating_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-07.png\"][/newsletter]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 6, 'Services', NULL, '<shortcode>[service-list background_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-01.png\" limit=\"6\"][/service-list]</shortcode><shortcode>[services title=\"The Pearl of the Adriatic.\" subtitle=\"Luxury Hotels &amp; Resorts\" description=\"**English translation:**{{NEWLINE}}{{NEWLINE}}Currently, there is no prominent decoration. Maecenas has created an appropriate pricing level. The overall link structure is quite solid, providing efficiency and harmony in connectivity. The operating system functions flexibly along the main connection flow. Users can make adjustments in a flexible manner. At present, the pathway has been opened, helping to improve oper\" left_image=\"rooms/168439420905-senna-hilltop-pool-villa-2-br-5.jpg\" right_floating_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-02.png\" button_label=\"Discover more\" button_url=\"/about-us\"][/services]</shortcode><shortcode>[booking-form title=\"Book A Room\" subtitle=\"Make Reservation\" description=\"Make your reservation quickly and conveniently in just a few simple steps. Choose your stay dates, select the room type that suits you, and enjoy a comfortable getaway with our professional service.\" image=\"places/1685507832restaurant-2.jpg\"][/booking-form]</shortcode><shortcode>[testimonials title=\"What Our Clients Says\" subtitle=\"Testimonial\" description=\"Discover genuine stories and reviews from guests who have experienced our services. Customer satisfaction is always our motivation to continuously improve and enhance the quality of our service.\" background_image=\"/backgrounds/testimonial-bg.png\" testimonial_ids=\"1,2,3,4,5,6\"][/testimonials]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 8, 'FAQ', NULL, '<shortcode>[faqs category_ids=\"1,2,3,4,5\"][/faqs]</shortcode><shortcode>[newsletter title=\"Get the Best Hotel Deals\" subtitle=\"Newsletter\" description=\"Discover attractive offers and special rates when booking a room at our hotel. Enjoy quality services along with many wonderful benefits for your vacation.\" background_color=\"#F7F5F1\" left_floating_image=\"backgrounds/an-img-07.png\"][/newsletter]</shortcode><shortcode>[teams title=\"Best Hotels\" subtitle=\"Our Team\" description=\"As a united team, we passionately craft your perfect stay, ensuring every detail reflects our commitment to exceptional hospitality.\" team_ids=\"1,2,3,4,5,6\" style=\"style-1\"][/teams]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 12, 'Privacy', NULL, '<div class=\"about-area5 about-p p-relative\"><div class=\"container pt-60 pb-90\"><div class=\"service-detail\"><div class=\"content-box\"><h2>Privacy Statement</h2><p>First things first – your privacy is important to us. That might be the kind of thing all these notices say, but we mean it. You place your trust in us by using us services and we value that trust. That means we’re committed to protecting and safeguarding your personal data. We act in our customers’ best interest and we are transparent about the processing of your personal data.</p><p>If you’ve used us before, you know that us services offers online travel-related services through our own websites and mobile apps, as well as other online platforms such as partners’ websites and social media. We’d like to point out that all the information you are about to read, generally applies to not one, not two, but all of these platforms.</p><p>If you’ve used us before, you know that us services offers online travel-related services through our own websites and mobile apps, as well as other online platforms such as partners’ websites and social media. We’d like to point out that all the information you are about to read, generally applies to not one, not two, but all of these platforms.</p><h2>Terms we use in this Privacy Statement</h2><p>\'Trip\' means the various different travel products and services that can be ordered, acquired, purchased, bought, paid, rented, provided, reserved, combined, or consummated by you from the Trip Provider.</p><p>\'Trip Provider\' means the provider of accommodation (e.g. hotel, motel, apartment, bed &amp; breakfast, landlord), attractions (e.g. (theme) parks, museums, sightseeing tours), transportation provider (e.g. car rentals, cruises, rail, airport rides, coach tours, transfers), tour operators, travel insurances and any other travel or related product or service as from time to time available for Trip Reservation on the platform.</p></div></div></div></div>'),
('en_US', 13, 'Term and Conditions', NULL, '<div class=\"about-area5 about-p p-relative\"><div class=\"container pt-60 pb-90\"><div class=\"service-detail\"><div class=\"content-box\"><h3>Definitions</h3><p>Some of the words you’ll see have very specific meanings, so please check out the ‘RioRelax dictionary’ at the end of these Terms.</p><h3>About these terms</h3><p>When you complete your Booking, you accept these Terms and any other terms that you’re provided with during the booking process.</p><p>The English version of these Terms is the original. If there’s any dispute about the Terms, or any mismatch between the Terms in English and in another language, the Terms as they appear in English will apply. (You can change the language at the top of this page.</p><h3>Our Platform</h3><p>We take reasonable care in providing our Platform, but we can’t guarantee that everything on it is accurate (we get information from the Service Providers). To the extent permitted by law, we can’t be held responsible for any errors, any interruptions, or any missing bits of information - although we will do everything we can to correct/fix them as soon as we can.</p><p>We will show you the offers that are available to you, in (what we think is) the right language for you. You can change to another language whenever you like.</p><h3>Prices</h3><p>When you make a Booking, you agree to pay the cost of the Travel Experience, including any charges and taxes that may apply.</p><p>Some of the prices you see may have been rounded to the nearest whole number. The price you pay will be based on the original, \'non-rounded\' price (although the actual difference will be tiny anyway).</p></div></div></div></div>'),
