('en_US', 7, 'cloud-pool', 'Cloud Pool is an infinity pool set amidst lush mountains and green valleys, where guests can immerse themselves in the refreshing water, enjoy the natural atmosphere, and admire peaceful moments surrounded by the beauty of nature.', '<p>During resort vacations, the swimming pool is always one of the amenities most loved by guests. It is not simply a place for swimming; in luxury resorts, pools are often designed as relaxing spaces where visitors can also admire the surrounding natural scenery. Cloud Pool is exactly such a place—an infinity pool designed in harmony with nature, offering guests a unique and refreshing relaxation experience.</p><p>Cloud Pool is located at an elevated position, opening up a wide view of the valley and the layers of lush green mountains. From here, guests can clearly feel the peacefulness of nature while looking down at vast forests and soft clouds drifting across the mountain peaks. The infinity-style design makes the water appear to extend endlessly toward the horizon, creating a seamless connection between people and nature.</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:1254/565;\" src=\"https://retreat.anduongliving.com/storage/1681381402rectangle-324.png\" alt=\"1681381402rectangle-324.png\" width=\"1254\" height=\"565\"></figure><p>As soon as guests arrive at the pool area, they will notice the fresh and cool atmosphere of the mountains. The gentle sound of wind through the trees, birds singing, and the quiet natural landscape help melt away daily stress. It is an ideal place to begin the day with a few relaxing laps in the pool or simply sit by the water and enjoy the tranquil surroundings.</p><p>In the early morning, Cloud Pool offers a particularly magical view as light mist covers the valley. The pool’s surface reflects the soft morning sunlight, creating a gentle and vibrant natural picture. This is also a favorite time for many guests to take photos or enjoy a cup of coffee in the peaceful setting.</p><p>As the sun rises higher, the pool area becomes more vibrant with bright sunshine and clear blue skies. The cool, refreshing water of the pool provides a pleasant escape from the heat of the day. Around the pool are thoughtfully arranged lounge areas where guests can relax, read a book, or simply enjoy their leisure time.</p><p>In the afternoon, Cloud Pool becomes especially romantic and impressive. As the sun gradually sets on the horizon, the sky transforms into warm shades of orange, yellow, and pink. The last sunlight reflecting on the water creates a breathtaking scene, bringing a sense of calm and serenity to everyone present.</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:916/539;\" src=\"https://retreat.anduongliving.com/storage/1722934877a-sea-of-cloud-from-our-terrace.jpg\" alt=\"1722934877a-sea-of-cloud-from-our-terrace.jpg\" width=\"916\" height=\"539\"></figure><p>The surrounding space of Cloud Pool is designed to offer maximum comfort for guests. Lounge chairs, resting areas, and open spaces allow everyone to enjoy nature in their own way. It is also a perfect place to chat with friends and family or simply spend quiet time alone.</p><p>Besides swimming and relaxing, Cloud Pool is also a favorite location for photography. With its vast natural backdrop and striking pool design, every corner here can become a beautiful photo spot. Pictures taken by the pool with mountains and blue skies in the background always convey a sense of elegance and tranquility.</p><p>Cloud Pool is open daily from 07:00 to 18:30, providing the perfect setting for guests to enjoy their holiday. Whether in the peaceful morning, the bright midday sun, or the romantic afternoon light, this place always offers memorable experiences.</p><p>With its elegant design, stunning location, and relaxing atmosphere surrounded by nature, Cloud Pool is not just a swimming pool but a special destination for those who want to enjoy the serenity and beauty of the mountains. 🌿💧</p>'),
('en_US', 8, 'orchild-spa', 'Orchid Spa is a wellness and relaxation space set amidst peaceful nature, where guests can experience therapeutic treatments that help restore energy and balance the body after busy days.', '<p>In modern life, with its fast pace and many pressures, taking time to care for oneself has become increasingly important. Spa treatments not only help the body relax but also bring balance to both physical and mental well-being. Orchid Spa was created with the goal of offering guests a peaceful space to rest, restore energy, and enjoy moments of true relaxation.</p><p>Orchid Spa is designed with inspiration from nature, creating a harmonious and gentle atmosphere. The architecture of the spa incorporates many natural materials such as wood, stone, and greenery, making the space feel warm and close to nature. As soon as guests enter the spa area, they can sense the calm and relaxation from the very first moments.</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:592/500;\" src=\"/storage/1681438650rectangle-464.png\" alt=\"1681438650rectangle-464.png\" width=\"592\" height=\"500\"></figure><p>The interior space of Orchid Spa is thoughtfully arranged to provide privacy and comfort for every guest. Soft lighting, the delicate scent of natural essential oils, and the gentle sounds of nature create a completely relaxing atmosphere. It is the ideal place to set aside the worries of daily life and spend time caring for yourself.</p><p>At Orchid Spa, guests can choose from a variety of wellness treatments. Popular services include relaxation massages, body care treatments, herbal therapies, and traditional healing methods. Each treatment is designed to deliver optimal results, helping the body relax and recover after stressful workdays or long journeys.</p><p>The therapists at the spa are professionally trained and always ready to provide attentive care to every guest. With skilled massage techniques and a deep understanding of the body, they help relieve tension, improve blood circulation, and bring a sense of comfort to the entire body.</p><p>One of the special features of Orchid Spa is the use of products derived from natural ingredients. Essential oils, herbs, and skincare products are carefully selected to provide the best results while remaining safe for the skin. The gentle fragrance of these natural oils helps guests feel relaxed and comfortable throughout the treatment.</p><p>More than just a place for body care, Orchid Spa is also a space where guests can rediscover balance within themselves. After each treatment, you will feel a sense of lightness and relaxation spreading throughout your body. Stress seems to fade away, replaced by a feeling of peace and renewed energy.</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:842/438;\" src=\"/storage/1681438738rectangle-469.png\" alt=\"1681438738rectangle-469.png\" width=\"842\" height=\"438\"></figure><p>The spa is also an ideal place to combine with other wellness activities such as meditation or relaxation after enjoying other facilities of the resort. Many guests choose to end a long day with a gentle massage treatment, allowing the body to fully relax before resting.</p><p>Orchid Spa not only offers high-quality wellness treatments but also creates a complete relaxation experience. The peaceful atmosphere, professional service, and harmonious connection with nature make it an ideal destination for those who want to restore their energy and regain balance in life.</p><p>With all these values, Orchid Spa is not simply a spa service but a comprehensive wellness journey where guests can enjoy moments of complete relaxation and return to a balanced state both physically and mentally.</p>'),
('en_US', 9, 'What is Senjuan?', NULL, '<p>Introducing Senjuan</p><p>A world-renowned Japanese resort, this inn offers private spaces with outdoor baths in each room, providing a healing experience through the breath of nature and genuine hospitality.</p><p>Our inn is situated along the Tanigawa River, with Mount Tanigawa as a backdrop, offering a tranquil and private setting.</p><p>Each uniquely designed room features an outdoor bath where you can enjoy the natural hot spring water flowing directly from the source.</p><p>We look forward to your arrival with exquisite cuisine using seasonal ingredients,</p><p>and genuine hospitality.</p><p>All rooms have private outdoor baths with freely flowing hot spring water. Enjoy luxurious relaxation and tranquility in your private space with panoramic views of Mount Tanigawa from your outdoor bath.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>A visual feast<br>Cuisine and sake crafted from fresh, locally sourced seasonal ingredients<br>Starting with beautifully presented appetizers, the meal features a variety of dishes prepared with carefully selected seasonal ingredients, including mountain specialties, river specialties, and Joshu beef.</p><p>Meals will be served in our 18 charming private dining rooms.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>Meticulous Design<br>To showcase the essence of a Japanese resort, we are committed to both design and service. Traditional Japanese architectural techniques and materials are incorporated throughout the project. The combination of modern architecture, such as the approximately 8-meter-high curved corridors, with traditional techniques like shoji kumiko partitions and lighting fixtures decorated with mica-printed washi paper, allows you to enjoy an extraordinary experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 10, 'What is Relais & Châteaux?', NULL, '<p>Relais &amp; Châteaux is an association founded in 1954, comprising approximately 540 leading luxury hotels and restaurants worldwide, all privately owned or family-run by hotel owners and chefs.</p><p>Membership requires a rigorous screening process, and the association is known as a symbol of high-end hospitality.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>From the vineyards of Napa Valley to the Provence region of France, the countless stunning beaches stretching along the Indian Ocean, and the traditional hot spring resorts of Japan, members of Relais &amp; Châteaux welcome you to many countries and regions around the world, inviting you to experience the wonderful lifestyle and attractions rooted in local culture and environment.</p><p>In Japan, there are 20 registered hotels and restaurants, including the Senjuan resort.</p><p>For more information, please see below.</p><p>Established in 1954, Relais &amp; Châteaux is a non-profit organization comprising 580 carefully selected hotels and restaurants worldwide.</p><p>Supported by independent hotel owners and chefs who share a strong belief in living in harmony with local communities, preserving the richness and diversity of culinary cultures, and fostering genuine relationships with guests, Relais &amp; Châteaux is present all over the world, from the vineyards of Napa Valley to the Provence of France, the countless stunning beaches along the Indian Ocean, and even the traditional hot spring resorts of Japan.</p><p>It is these unique experiences, allowing guests to feel the distinctive culture and history of each place, and the memories that can only be created there, that draw people in.</p><p>The members of Relais &amp; Châteaux are committed to preserving and nurturing the richness and diversity of culinary cultures and the hospitality traditions that the world is proud of.</p><p>In 2014, UNESCO declared the vision of 20 Relais &amp; Châteaux to be actively involved in protecting local history and the environment.</p><p>Established in 1954, Relais &amp; Châteaux is an association of 580 unique hotels and restaurants worldwide, owned and operated by independent entrepreneurs – often families – who are passionate about their craft and deeply committed to building warm, lasting relationships with their customers.</p><p>Present on five continents, from the vineyards of Napa Valley to Provence and the beaches of the Indian Ocean, Relais &amp; Châteaux invites people around the globe to enjoy extraordinary culinary journeys, discover the unique art of living ingrained in each local culture, and share an unparalleled, unforgettable experience.</p><p>Members of Relais &amp; Châteaux protect and promote the richness and diversity of culinary and hospitality traditions around the world, ensuring their continued flourishing. They are also committed to preserving local heritage and the environment, as outlined in the association\'s Vision presented to UNESCO in November 2014.</p>'),
('en_US', 11, 'Sisters\' Inn: Ryokan Tanigawa', NULL, '<p>Sister Inns: Ryokan Tanigawa</p><p>A \"Second Home\" for Our Guests<br>Dedicated Hospitality, a Spiritual Home<br>Ryokan Tanigawa aspires to be a \"second home\" for our guests. When welcoming guests, we always do so with the same warmth as welcoming a long-lost family member.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:728/483;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_pic01.jpg\" alt=\"姉妹館 旅館たにがわ\" width=\"728\" height=\"483\"></figure><p>A relaxing hot spring inn where you can enjoy the seasonal scenery of Tanigawadake and immerse yourself in nature. Ryokan Tanigawa is located in a tranquil hot spring resort at the foot of the southern slopes of Mount Tanigawa.</p><p>As the slogan \"Mount Tanigawa seems within reach\" suggests, Mount Tanigawa, viewed from the Tanigawa area, takes on a different beauty in each season: lingering snow and cherry blossoms, lush greenery and cool breezes, vibrant autumn foliage and a vast, shimmering silver landscape. Situated within Joshin\'etsu Kogen National Park, the modern building blends seamlessly into the peaceful Tanigawa Onsen area, a setting that evokes strong emotions in many visitors.</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shizen01.jpg\" alt=\"谷川岳の四季折々の景観を満喫できる心安らぐ温泉宿\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shizen02.jpg\" alt=\"谷川岳の四季折々の景観を満喫できる心安らぐ温泉宿\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"></p><p>Enjoy the seasonal flavors of Joshu at four different tea houses, each offering a unique culinary experience.</p><p>With the motto \"health and deliciousness,\" our chefs and staff work diligently every day to ensure you can fully enjoy the seasonal flavors that Tanigawa has cultivated.</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shoku01.jpg\" alt=\"それぞれ異なる4つの茶屋で、上州の旬の味覚に舌鼓\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shoku02.jpg\" alt=\"それぞれ異なる4つの茶屋で、上州の旬の味覚に舌鼓\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"></p><p>Enjoy the abundant hot springs and their amazing benefits, with over 20 different health effects.</p><p>Tanigawa Onsen has been continuously flowing for hundreds of years since it first erupted in this area during the Edo period. The water is crystal clear, has a high flow rate, is clean, and of high quality because it comes from a private source. This hot spring also has over 20 therapeutic properties and can be used as a therapeutic bath.</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_onsen01.jpg\" alt=\"豊富な湯量と20種類以上の効能をもつ滋養溢れる温泉\" width=\"303\" height=\"185\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_onsen02.jpg\" alt=\"豊富な湯量と20種類以上の効能をもつ滋養溢れる温泉\" width=\"303\" height=\"185\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p>'),
('en_US', 12, 'Special room with outdoor bathroom (SP)', NULL, '<p>Surrounded by the majestic natural beauty of Tanigawa year-round,</p><p>All rooms feature private outdoor baths with free-flowing hot spring water and views of Mount Tanigawa.</p><p>All rooms at our inn have private outdoor baths, allowing you to enjoy the hot springs in complete privacy.</p><p>This is a quintessential example of a \"Japanese resort.\"</p><p>All rooms are equipped with private outdoor baths with free-flowing hot spring water, and you can enjoy panoramic views of Mount Tanigawa from both your room and the outdoor bath.</p><p>In a spacious 1000 tsubo (approximately 3300 square meter) building, there are only 18 rooms, allowing you to relax in privacy, where you can spend quiet and peaceful time in your private outdoor bath, which you can use anytime and as often as you like,</p><p>and in a room with spacious and thoughtfully designed furnishings.</p><p>Surrounded by the majestic natural beauty of Tanigawa, which changes its appearance with each season, enjoy a wonderful time of relaxation and rejuvenation.</p><p>SP Special Room with Outdoor Bath<br>Spacious interior, meticulously designed down to the smallest detail, along with a large outdoor bath, creates a feeling of luxurious privacy. [Layout]<br>12.5 tatami mat Japanese-style room + 8 tatami mat Japanese-style room + tea room + spacious veranda +<br>Outdoor bath with free-flowing hot spring water<br>Eight steps lead up to the room.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 13, 'Japanese-style S-room with outdoor bathtub', NULL, '<p>Japanese-style room with open-air bath (S size)<br>This is a semi-special room with a spacious Japanese-style room, an adjoining room, and a private open-air bath. [Layout]<br>12.5 tatami mat Japanese-style room + 8 tatami mat adjoining room + wide veranda +<br>Private open-air bath with free-flowing hot spring water<br>There are 8 steps leading up to the room.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 14, 'Room A is Japanese-style with an outdoor bathtub, sauna, and terrace.', NULL, '<p>Japanese-style room A with open-air bath, sauna, and terrace<br>This Japanese-style room is spacious, including the adjoining room, and is a popular room with a large terrace where you can enjoy a panoramic view of Mt. Tanigawa and a sauna for one person. It is a location where you can enjoy the ultimate retreat while gazing at Mt. Tanigawa and listening to the clear stream of Tanigawa, with a private open-air bath and sauna. [Layout]<br>12.5 tatami mat Japanese-style room + 4.5 tatami mat adjoining room + wide veranda + terrace +<br>Sauna (for 1 person) + private open-air bath with free-flowing hot spring water<br>There are 8 steps leading up to the room.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 15, 'Japanese-style Room B with an outdoor bathtub and terrace.', NULL, '<p>Japanese-style room B with open-air bath and terrace<br>This popular room features a 12.5 tatami mat Japanese-style room and a private open-air bath, plus a terrace where you can enjoy the clear stream of Tanigawa right in front of you. You can relax in a great location while being soothed by the gentle murmur of the stream. [Layout]<br>12.5 tatami mat Japanese-style room + wide veranda + terrace +<br>Private open-air bath with free-flowing hot spring water<br>There are 8 steps leading up to the room.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong4\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 16, 'A room with a Japanese-Western style and an outdoor bathtub.', NULL, '<p>Japanese-Western Style Room with Outdoor Bath<br>This room features a Japanese-style room and a spacious double bedroom, along with an outdoor bath. Enjoy the fresh air from the large windows and the outdoor bath. [Layout]<br>Western Style Room (40 m²) + Japanese Style Room (8 tatami mats) +<br>Outdoor bath with free-flowing hot spring water in the room.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong5\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 17, 'dinner', NULL, '<figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_1.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_1.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\">Examples of appetizers</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_2.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_2.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\">Example of sashimi</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_3.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_3.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\">An example of a bowl</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_4.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_4.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\">Examples of stews</p>'),
('en_US', 18, 'breakfast', NULL, '<shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"bua-sang\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>Breakfast also features plenty of seasonal, locally sourced ingredients, emphasizing the natural flavors of the ingredients. Dishes packed with fresh vegetables are gentle on the body and invigorate you.</p>'),
('en_US', 19, 'Restaurant', NULL, '<p>This is an example of our dining area.</p><p>Enjoy delicious meals to your liking in a sophisticatedly designed private space. High ceilings and a spacious feel.</p><p>A private room with high ceilings and a spacious feel, featuring a recessed dining table and comfortable sofas.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:1040/600;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine05_pic01.jpg\" alt=\"お食事処 彩華\" width=\"1040\" height=\"600\"></figure>'),
('en_US', 20, 'Suzumushi no Yu (Cricket Hot Spring)', NULL, '<p>Experience superior relaxation<br>Spend luxurious time<br>Located west of the Minakami Onsen area, Tanigawa Onsen has been continuously flowing since the Edo period,<br>and has long been cherished by the people of this heavy snowfall region.<br>The hot spring water at Senjuan is a gentle, hypotonic, weakly alkaline spring. Enjoy the fresh air amidst the clear stream and greenery of Tanigawa in our open-air bath, the scent of cypress in our indoor bath, and a walking bath where you can relax and chat.<br>Above all, you can enjoy a luxurious and comfortable time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 21, 'Ichinokura Large Public Bathhouse', NULL, '<p>The sauna features walls made of Binchotan charcoal, providing superior insulation.</p><p>You can choose your preferred temperature, from 70°C on the lower level to 90°C on the upper level.</p><p>There is also a relaxation area by the window where you can unwind and enjoy the lush green scenery outside.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 22, 'Hotaru no Yu Outdoor Bathhouse', NULL, '<p>Enjoy the liberating feeling of the open-air bath overlooking the Tanigawa Valley. Relax in the bath while feeling the pleasant breeze blowing across the valley.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 23, '大きな公衆浴場、千の倉', NULL, '<p>お肌に優しく、女性にもおすすめの低温「ミストサウナ」を併設しております。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 24, 'Walk-in bathtubs are only for use in the summer.', NULL, '<p>Next to the spa room is a walking bath with a stream flowing in front of it, allowing you to relax while enjoying the forest air. The comfortable water temperature of 38 to 41 degrees Celsius will soothe your fatigue.</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('en_US', 25, 'SPA', NULL, '<p>Relax your body and release your breath in this truly holistic SPA experience.</p><p>Focus on total body relaxation.</p><p>The rich light, sound, and aroma of Tanigawa nature,<br>revitalize the comfort of the five senses,<br>and nurture harmony between nature, body, and mind…</p><p>The energy of Tanigawa water and wild plants<br>The trees and flowers of Tanigawa mountain<br>Elements of nature</p><p>Based on the principles of Yin and Yang and the Five Elements, we have combined Tanigawa nature with traditional Japanese techniques.</p><p>Immerse yourself in nature, use traditional Japanese techniques, breathe deeply, and experience inner peace.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"spa\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>Nature Treatment<br>Stretching, massage, and compression techniques directly relieve muscle tension, and a special natural gel made with stream water and medicinal herbs is used to improve circulation.</p><p>60-minute course / ¥19,800 (tax included)</p><p>90-minute course / ¥29,700 (tax included)</p><p>*Treatment will be tailored to your physical condition based on a consultation.</p><p>Special evening program<br>Deep sleep therapy<br>Gently massages the back, head, neck, and décolleté, promoting deep relaxation and quality sleep.<br>Natural blessings gently soothe your tired mind and body.</p><p>30-minute course / ¥15,400 (tax included)</p><p>60-minute course / ¥22,000 (tax included)</p><p>90-minute course / ¥33,000 (tax included)</p><p>*Treatment will be tailored to your physical condition based on a consultation.<br>Please feel free to consult or inquire for more details when making a reservation.</p>'),
('ja', 9, 'センジュアンとは何ですか？', NULL, '<p>千住庵のご紹介</p><p>世界的に有名な日本のリゾートホテル、千住庵は、各部屋に露天風呂を備えたプライベート空間をご提供し、自然の息吹と真心のこもったおもてなしで、心身ともに癒されるひとときをお過ごしいただけます。</p><p>当旅館は谷川沿いに位置し、谷川岳を背景に、静かでプライベートな空間をお楽しみいただけます。</p><p>それぞれ個性的なデザインの客室には、源泉直送の天然温泉が楽しめる露天風呂が備わっています。</p><p>旬の食材を使った絶品料理と、真心のこもったおもてなしで、皆様のお越しを心よりお待ちしております。</p><p>全室に、湧き出る天然温泉が楽しめるプライベート露天風呂をご用意しております。露天風呂からは谷川岳のパノラマビューが広がり、贅沢なリラクゼーションと静寂をご堪能いただけます。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>視覚的にも楽しめる美食体験<br>新鮮な地元産の旬の食材をふんだんに使った料理と日本酒<br>美しく盛り付けられた前菜から始まり、山の幸、川の幸、上州牛など、厳選された旬の食材を使った多彩な料理をご堪能いただけます。</p><p>お食事は、趣のある18室の個室でご提供いたします。</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>&nbsp;</p><p>細部にまでこだわったデザイン<br>日本のリゾートの真髄を表現するため、デザインとサービスの両方にこだわりました。伝統的な日本の建築技術と素材を随所に取り入れています。高さ約8メートルの曲線を描く回廊など、現代的な建築と、障子組子や雲母模様の和紙で装飾された照明器具といった伝統的な技法が融合し、格別な体験をお届けします。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 10, 'ルレ・エ・シャトーとは何ですか？', NULL, '<p>ルレ・エ・シャトーは1954年に設立された協会で、世界中の約540軒の一流高級ホテルとレストランが加盟しています。これらのホテルとレストランはすべて、オーナーやシェフが個人経営または家族経営で運営しています。</p><p>加盟には厳格な審査プロセスが必要で、ルレ・エ・シャトーは最高級のおもてなしの象徴として知られています。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"y-tuong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>ナパバレーのブドウ畑からフランスのプロヴァンス地方、インド洋沿いに広がる数々の美しいビーチ、そして日本の伝統的な温泉地まで、ルレ・エ・シャトー加盟ホテルは世界各地の多くの国と地域でお客様をお迎えし、その土地の文化と環境に根ざした素晴らしいライフスタイルと魅力をご体験いただけるようご案内いたします。</p><p>日本には千住庵リゾートを含む20軒のホテルとレストランが登録されています。</p><p>詳細は下記をご覧ください。</p><p>1954年に設立されたルレ・エ・シャトーは、世界中の厳選された580軒のホテルとレストランからなる非営利団体です。</p><p>地域社会との調和、豊かな食文化の多様性の継承、そしてゲストとの真摯な関係構築を強く信じる独立系ホテルオーナーやシェフたちに支えられ、ルレ・エ・シャトーは世界各地に展開しています。ナパ・バレーのブドウ畑からフランスのプロヴァンス、インド洋沿岸の数々の美しいビーチ、そして日本の伝統的な温泉地まで、その範囲は多岐にわたります。</p><p>ゲストがそれぞれの土地ならではの文化や歴史を感じ、そこでしか生まれない思い出を作れる、こうした特別な体験こそが人々を惹きつけるのです。</p><p>ルレ・エ・シャトーの加盟ホテルは、世界が誇る豊かな食文化とホスピタリティの伝統を守り、育むことに尽力しています。</p><p>2014年、ユネスコは、ルレ・エ・シャトー20軒が地域の歴史と環境保護に積極的に取り組むというビジョンを掲げました。</p><p>1954年に設立されたルレ・エ・シャトーは、世界中に580軒の個性豊かなホテルとレストランが集まる協会です。これらのホテルやレストランは、独立系起業家（多くは家族経営）によって所有・運営されており、彼らは自らの仕事に情熱を注ぎ、お客様との温かく永続的な関係構築に深く尽力しています。</p><p>ナパ・バレーのブドウ畑からプロヴァンス、インド洋のビーチまで、5大陸に展開するルレ・エ・シャトーは、世界中の人々を特別な食の旅へと誘い、それぞれの地域文化に根付いた独自のライフスタイルを発見し、比類のない忘れられない体験を共有します。</p><p>ルレ・エ・シャトーの加盟ホテルは、世界各地の豊かで多様な食文化とホスピタリティの伝統を守り、促進し、その繁栄を確実なものにしています。また、2014年11月にユネスコに提出された協会のビジョンに明記されているように、地域の遺産と環境の保護にも積極的に取り組んでいます。</p>'),
('ja', 11, '姉妹の宿 旅館谷川', NULL, '<p>姉妹旅館：谷川旅館</p><p>お客様にとっての「第二の我が家」<br>心温まるおもてなし、心の安らぎ<br>谷川旅館は、お客様にとって「第二の我が家」となることを目指しています。お客様をお迎えする時は、まるで長年会っていなかった家族を迎えるような温かさで、心を込めておもてなしいたします。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:728/483;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_pic01.jpg\" alt=\"姉妹館 旅館たにがわ\" width=\"728\" height=\"483\"></figure><p>谷川岳の四季折々の美しい景色を堪能し、自然に身を委ねられる、心安らぐ温泉旅館。谷川旅館は、谷川岳南斜面の麓に位置する静寂な温泉地にあります。</p><p>「谷川岳が手の届くところにある」というキャッチフレーズが示すように、谷川エリアから眺める谷川岳は、四季折々に異なる美しさを見せてくれます。雪化粧と桜、緑豊かな木々と涼やかな風、鮮やかな紅葉、そして銀色に輝く広大な景色。上信越高原国立公園内に位置するモダンな建物は、静寂に包まれた谷川温泉エリアに溶け込み、訪れる多くの人々に深い感動を与えます。</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shizen01.jpg\" alt=\"谷川岳の四季折々の景観を満喫できる心安らぐ温泉宿\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shizen02.jpg\" alt=\"谷川岳の四季折々の景観を満喫できる心安らぐ温泉宿\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"></p><p>上州の旬の味覚を、それぞれ個性豊かな4つの茶室でお楽しみください。</p><p>「健康と美味しさ」をモットーに、当茶室の料理人やスタッフは、谷川が丹精込めて育てた旬の味覚を存分に味わっていただけるよう、日々心を込めて調理しています。</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shoku01.jpg\" alt=\"それぞれ異なる4つの茶屋で、上州の旬の味覚に舌鼓\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_shoku02.jpg\" alt=\"それぞれ異なる4つの茶屋で、上州の旬の味覚に舌鼓\" width=\"303\" height=\"195\"></p><p>20種類以上の健康効果を誇る、豊富な温泉と素晴らしい効能をご堪能ください。</p><p>谷川温泉は、江戸時代にこの地で初めて湧き出て以来、数百年にわたり湧き続けています。源泉は私有のため、水は澄み渡り、水量も豊富で、清らかで高品質です。20種類以上の効能を持ち、療養風呂としてもご利用いただけます。</p><p><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_onsen01.jpg\" alt=\"豊富な湯量と20種類以上の効能をもつ滋養溢れる温泉\" width=\"303\" height=\"185\"><img src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/concept/concept05_onsen02.jpg\" alt=\"豊富な湯量と20種類以上の効能をもつ滋養溢れる温泉\" width=\"303\" height=\"185\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `posts_translations` (`lang_code`, `posts_id`, `name`, `description`, `content`) VALUES
('ja', 12, '屋外バスルーム付き特別室（SP）', NULL, '<p>谷川の雄大な自然美に囲まれた、一年を通して美しい景色が広がる宿です。</p><p>全室に、谷川岳の眺望を楽しめる、湧き水が流れ落ちる専用露天風呂を完備しています。</p><p>当旅館の全客室には専用露天風呂があり、プライベートな空間で温泉を心ゆくまでお楽しみいただけます。</p><p>まさに「日本のリゾート」の真髄を体現した宿です。</p><p>全室に湧き水が流れ落ちる専用露天風呂を備え、客室からも露天風呂からも谷川岳のパノラマビューをお楽しみいただけます。</p><p>広々とした1000坪（約3300平方メートル）の建物には、わずか18室のみ。プライベートな空間でゆったりとお過ごしいただけます。いつでもお好きな時にご利用いただける専用露天風呂で、静かで穏やかなひとときをお過ごしください。</p><p>広々とした客室には、細部までこだわった家具が備えられています。</p><p><br>四季折々に表情を変える谷川の雄大な自然美に囲まれ、至福のリラクゼーションとリフレッシュのひとときをお過ごしください。</p><p>SPスペシャルルーム（露天風呂付き）<br>細部にまでこだわった広々とした室内空間と、ゆったりとした露天風呂が、贅沢なプライベート空間を演出します。【間取り】<br>12.5畳和室＋8畳和室＋茶室＋広々とした縁側＋<br>湧き水が流れ出る露天風呂<br>客室へは8段の階段を上ります。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 13, '露天風呂付きの和風Sルーム', NULL, '<p>露天風呂付き和室（Sサイズ）<br>広々とした和室、隣室、専用露天風呂を備えたセミスペシャルタイプのお部屋です。【間取り】<br>和室（12.5畳）＋隣室（8畳）＋広い縁側＋<br>湧き水が流れ出る専用露天風呂<br>お部屋へは8段の階段を上っていただきます。</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>&nbsp;</p>'),
('ja', 14, 'A室は、露天風呂、サウナ、テラスを備えた和室です。', NULL, '<p>露天風呂・サウナ・テラス付き和室A<br>隣室を含む広々とした和室で、谷川岳のパノラマビューを楽しめる大きなテラスとプライベートサウナが人気のお部屋です。谷川岳を眺めながら、谷川渓流の清らかなせせらぎに耳を傾け、プライベート露天風呂とサウナで至福のひとときをお過ごしいただけます。【間取り】<br>和室（12.5畳）＋隣室（4.5畳）＋広い縁側＋テラス＋<br>サウナ（1名様用）＋天然温泉のプライベート露天風呂<br>お部屋へは8段の階段を上っていただきます。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 15, '露天風呂とテラス付きの和室B。', NULL, '<p>露天風呂とテラス付き和室B<br>人気のこのお部屋は、広々とした12.5畳の和室と専用露天風呂、そして目の前に清らかな谷川が流れるテラスを備えています。せせらぎの音に誘われながら、至福のひとときをお過ごしいただけます。【間取り】<br>12.5畳和室＋広々としたテラス＋パティオ＋<br>湧き水が流れ出る専用露天風呂<br>お部屋へは8段の階段を上っていただきます。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong4\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 16, '和洋折衷様式の客室と露天風呂。', NULL, '<p>露天風呂付き和洋折衷室<br>このお部屋は、和室と広々としたダブルベッドルームに加え、露天風呂を備えています。大きな窓から吹き込む爽やかな風と露天風呂をお楽しみください。【間取り】<br>洋室（40㎡）＋和室（8畳）＋<br>室内露天風呂（天然温泉）</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"phong5\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 17, 'dinner', NULL, '<figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_1.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_1.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(247,254,251);color:rgb(22,29,28);font-size:11px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:monospace;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">前菜一例</span></span></p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_2.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_2.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(247,254,251);color:rgb(22,29,28);font-size:11px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:monospace;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">お造り一例</span></span></p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_3.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_3.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(247,254,251);color:rgb(22,29,28);font-size:11px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:monospace;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">お椀一例</span></span></p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:640/427;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine11_4.JPG\" alt=\"cuisine11_4.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(247,254,251);color:rgb(22,29,28);font-size:11px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:monospace;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:pre-wrap;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">煮物一例</span></span></p>'),
('ja', 18, '朝食', NULL, '<shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"bua-sang\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>朝食には、旬の地元産食材をふんだんに使用し、素材本来の風味を最大限に引き出しています。新鮮な野菜をたっぷり使った料理は健康的で、エネルギー補給にも役立ちます。</p>'),
('ja', 19, 'レストラン', NULL, '<p>こちらは当ホテルのダイニングエリアの一例です。</p><p>洗練されたデザインのプライベート空間で、お好みの美味しいお食事をお楽しみください。高い天井と広々とした空間が魅力です。</p><p>高い天井とゆったりとした空間が特徴のプライベートルームには、埋め込み式のダイニングテーブルと快適なソファが備えられています。</p><figure class=\"image\"><img style=\"aspect-ratio:1040/600;\" src=\"https://www.senjyuan.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/senjyuan/lib/images/cuisine/cuisine05_pic01.jpg\" alt=\"お食事処 彩華\" width=\"1040\" height=\"600\"></figure>'),
('ja', 20, '鈴虫の湯（こおろぎの湯）', NULL, '<p>上質なリラクゼーションを体感<br>贅沢な時間を過ごす<br>水上温泉郷の西方に位置する谷川温泉は江戸時代からこんこんと湧き続け、<br>豪雪地帯のみなさまに古くから愛されてきました。<br>仙寿庵の湯は、肌にやさしい低張性弱アルカリ性温泉でございます。谷川の清流と緑の中で新鮮な空気とともに<br>愉しめる露天風呂、檜の香りが愉しめる内湯、談笑しながらほっとしたひとときを過ごせる歩行湯など、<br>何よりも贅沢で心地いい時間を愉しめます。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi1\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 21, '一ノ倉大銭湯', NULL, '<p>サウナの壁は備長炭を使用しており、優れた断熱性を備えています。</p><p>温度は下階の70℃から上階の90℃まで、お好みに合わせてお選びいただけます。</p><p>窓際にはリラックススペースがあり、緑豊かな景色を眺めながらゆったりとおくつろぎいただけます。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi2\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 22, '蛍の湯 屋外浴場', NULL, '<p>解放感に溢れた谷川渓谷を望む露天風呂。谷川を渡る心地よい風を湯船でお愉しみください。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 23, 'Large public bathhouse, Sen no Kura', NULL, '<p>We also have a low-temperature mist sauna, which is gentle on the skin and highly recommended for women.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 24, 'ウォークインタイプの浴槽は夏季のみ使用可能です。', NULL, '<p>スパルーム横には、目の前を谷川が流れる歩行湯があり、森林浴とともにリラックスできます。 38度〜41度と心地よいお湯に疲れも癒やされます。</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"songhoi3\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode>'),
('ja', 25, 'SPA', NULL, '<p>心身をリラックスさせ、呼吸を整える、真にホリスティックなスパ体験をお楽しみください。</p><p>全身のリラクゼーションに焦点を当てます。</p><p>谷川の豊かな光、音、そして香りが、<br>五感を活性化させ、<br>自然、身体、そして心の調和を育みます。</p><p>谷川の水と野草のエネルギー<br>谷川の山々の木々と花々<br>自然の要素<br>陰陽五行の原理に基づき、谷川の自然と日本の伝統技法を融合させました。</p><p>自然に身を委ね、日本の伝統技法を用い、深く呼吸し、心の平安を体験してください。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><shortcode>[simple-slider key=\"spa\"][/simple-slider]</shortcode><p>ネイチャートリートメント<br>ストレッチ・もみほぐし・圧迫法で筋肉の緊張を直接ほぐし、<br>谷川の水と薬草で作られた特製ナチュラルジェルを使い、身体のめぐりを整えます。</p><p>60分コース/￥19,800（税込）</p><p>90分コース/￥29,700（税込）</p><p>※カウンセリングを基に、お身体の状態に合わせた施術を行います。</p><p>夜限定の特別プログラム<br>Deep sleep therapy<br>背中、頭、首、デコルテをメインに優しくほぐし、<br>深いリラクゼーションと良質な睡眠を促します。<br>疲れた心と身体に、自然の恵みで優しく寄り添います。</p><p>30分コース/￥15,400（税込）</p><p>60分コース/￥22,000（税込）</p><p>90分コース/￥33,000（税込）</p><p>※カウンセリングを基に、お身体の状態に合わせた施術を行います。<br>詳しくはご予約時にお気軽にご相談、お問い合わせください。</p>');
