(210, 'theme-riorelax-en_US-vi-cancellation', '<p>We’re pleased to offer a full refund of the booking amount for cancellations made <strong>14 days or more</strong> before the scheduled check-in date. This generous window provides you with the flexibility to adjust your plans without any financial repercussions.<p>', '2026-03-12 03:03:04', '2026-03-13 01:07:03'),
